snippet.title: Parappa the Rapper PSP - Stage 2 Remix A (1080p)
snippet.description:
Stage 2 Music A - You Guys Sit in the Back (Instructor Mooselini's RAP)

For the Parappa the Rapper re-release on the PSP, they added several remixed versions of the songs as DLC. Stage one got four new backing tracks, while stages 2-5 each got one new version.
Watch out for Prince Fleaswallow hitch-hiking.

It didn't look like anyone else had uploaded any footage of these to YouTube, so here we go.

Join as a member: https://www.youtube.com/phizzy/join
Patreon (monthly support): http://patreon.com/phizzy
PayPal (one-off donations): https://www.paypal.me/phizzy
Please consider donating to support the channel.

Part 5/8 of a series of Parappa the Rapper Official DLC Remixes for the PSP version.

Part 6: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VO4N8nDC89Y&list=PLUHieWXpUgH8P-_GxczYiuiCSFo9PmTvp&index=6
Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLUHieWXpUgH8P-_GxczYiuiCSFo9PmTvp

To download the free DLC songs for Parappa PSP, you can find them here, as they're no longer available officially from Sony:
